posting_body: ['MUST HAVE STRONG CREDIT!', 'NO EVICTIONS!', 'NO CRIMINAL RECORDS!', 'NO EXCEPTIONS!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!', 'CALL NOW!!!!!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!!', 'Email Me, Call Me, or Text!!!!', 'Shawn Kaminsky', 'show contact info', 'Village of Sandalwood Lakes South - 2 Bedroom / 2.5 Bath TOWNHOUSE with view of lake and fountain.', 'Features include; tile thru-out, two bedrooms each with their own en suite bath, primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and bath has dual sinks, washer & dryer; accordion hurricane shutters, fenced patio is perfect for entertaining & barbecues.', 'Community Amenities include Scenic Lake views, Pools, Tennis, Pickleball, Racquetball Courts, Playgrounds, & Exercise Trails.', "Located approximately 1.5 miles to ''The Ballpark of the Palm Beaches'' Spring Training Home to the Washington Nationals & Houston Astros.", "MOVE-IN REQUIRES: First Month, Last Month & Security Deposit (equal to one month's rent), in addition HOA charges $150 non-refundable appl fee per adult and $250 non-refundable admin fee."]
